-13/ty-article/.premium/battles-with-hamas-leave-scorched-land-the-wars-heavy-toll-on-israeli-nature/0000018d-a17d-d747-a78f-ff7dc2ed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部男子被枪杀；二月阿拉伯以色列社会第九名凶杀案受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-israels-north-ninth-homicide-victim-in-arab-israeli-society-in-february/0000018d-a168-d416-a3ed-edfa0f970000</link><description>纳比·塔巴拉尼 (Nabih Tabarani) 被发现在该市的一处观景台附近中枪，就在他正在行驶的车辆旁边。警方不认识他</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 08:03:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-israels-north-ninth-homicide-victim-in-arab-israeli-society-in-february/0000018d-a168-d416-a3ed-edfa0f970000</guid></item></channel></rss>